      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "\t- Structural tags in HTML define the basic structure of a webpage. The
    <html> tag wraps the entire document and tells the browser that the content is
    an HTML page, the <head> tag contains important information about the page such
    as the title and metadata, and the <body> tag holds all the visible content that
    appears on the screen."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
